🎯 Hangman Game in Java
A simple console-based Hangman game built with Java.
Try to guess the hidden word one letter at a time before the hangman is complete!

📌 Features
Built entirely in Java (no external libraries).

Word is randomly chosen from a predefined list.

Shows the current state of the guessed word (e.g., h _ n g _ a _).

Limits the number of wrong attempts.

Displays win/lose message based on your performance.

🧰 Tech Stack
Language: Java

Platform: Console (Terminal)

